Dr Neha has a calm, friendly and scientific approach. Dr Neha, Dr Srihari and Dr Fawad did an amazing job on my elderly father's teeth. They installed a full new set of teeth on implants that looks great and functions perfectly. It was particularly complex due to my father's age, Parkinsons-related tremors and other health issues. Their patience helped him remain calm throughout the procedures. 

Thanks to this procedure he is finally able to eat solid food after a year and this has helped his overall recovery. 

We are very grateful to Dr Neha, Dr Srihari and Dr Fawad and it is due to their skills, knowledge and the efforts they went to above and beyond (including coming home when my father could not travel) that makes medicine such a noble profession. 

I strongly recommend Dr Neha and her colleagues.

It was so perfect and everything was right. I had pain in my wisdom teeth over last 6-8 months. I was so very concerned and afraid to visit a dentist. Dr Neha has been very friendly, she diagnosed the problem well and explained the different options possible. The wisdom teeth had been problematic over 6-8 months and extraction was one good option. The entire procedure was made as comfortable as possible. I am happy now that the extraction was done well, stitches removed after one week and I am all good now. The place is very clean, hygienic and bright. The doctors are super experts and support stuff know what they need to do. ******** **** ***** *** *** ****** ***********

Patient is a senior citizen and she suggested things that we should do to avoid any damage in future because of old age and asked us to be proactive. That was quite useful in terms of planning. Clinic is well equipped and they are taking all covid precautions.
